{"id":256595,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/global-voices-柬埔寨：红色高棉下的生活/","date":"2012-10-12T06:30:12Z","modified":"2012-10-12T06:30:12Z","title":"Global Voices | 柬埔寨：红色高棉下的生活","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>我出生在1977年。我妈跟我说，那时候很难找到食物给我吃。他们强迫人民在稻田劳动，却不准他们吃任何东西，只给他们一碗粥。那便是<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B3%A2%E5%B0%94%E5%B8%83%E7%89%B9\">波布</a>政权。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Santel Phin<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://khmerbird.com/news/politic/my-understanding-about-pol-pot-and-khmer-rouge.html\">描述</a>了1970年代许多柬埔寨人在红色高棉统治下的生活。</p>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/mong/\" title=\"文章导读 Mong Palatino\">Mong Palatino</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/ameli/\" title=\"文章导读 Ameli\">Ameli</a></span></span>  · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2012/10/11/cambodia-life-under-the-khmer-rouge-regime/\" title=\"阅读原文  en\">阅读原文  en</a></span> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2012/10/12/11688/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E6%9F%AC%E5%9F%94%E5%AF%A8%EF%BC%9A%E7%BA%A2%E8%89%B2%E9%AB%98%E6%A3%89%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F10%2F12%2F11688%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F10%2F12%2F11688%2F&#038;desc=%E6%9F%AC%E5%9F%94%E5%AF%A8%EF%BC%9A%E7%BA%A2%E8%89%B2%E9%AB%98%E6%A3%89%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=